<h4 id="termux-terminal-emulator-and-linux-environment">Termux (Terminal Emulator and Linux Environment)</h4>
<p>Termux is a Linux Terminal emulator. You can run standard Linux programs on it like you would on your linux terminal. It comes with the Debian package installer Advanced Packaging Tools (apt) which you can use to install most of the popular Linux programs out there. As you can imagine, the app is pretty awesome and personally it is my favorite ğŸ android app of all time.</p>

<h4 id="hackers-keyboard">Hackerâ€™s Keyboard</h4>
